text: Isak Stianson Pedersen (born 4 June 1997) is an Icelandic cross-country skier. He competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Icelandic male cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross- country skiers of Iceland
